Class AID

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.trendit.basesdk.utils.BaseParcelable
      • com.trendit.basesdk.device.emv.AID
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    public class AID
extends BaseParcelable
implements android.os.Parcelable
    application identifier；AID It consists of a registered application providing a trademark (RID) and a special application identifier extension (Pix). The AID parameters are stored in a file and will not be lost when the application is restarted.
